Subject: [PATCH 130/130] =?UTF-8?q?config:=20regenerar=20el=20defconfig=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E2=80=94=20le=20faltaban=20codec,=20PCIe,=20VPU=20y=20joydev?=
